name: Squid Smack
summary: Swim with your hands as a squid in this fun multiplayer underwater exploration. Ink, Smack other squids with your smack ability to send them flying across the map, Cloak to surfaces, find your way to the shipwreck to, fight sharks, visit the island, cook food at the Underwater Campfire, visit the Underworld and mine gems, and more! Watch out for other squids who might be tempted to use their smacking abilities on you! Oh... And Don't get Eaten... 2 Developers, Husband and Wife
